{
  "stem": "13313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would simply be taken for a while to help the Germans with their war effort.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was an organization called Organisation Todt, T-O-D-T, under Albert Speer, I believe, which really was always in charge of slave labor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first-- the people who were rounded up in our town were shipped off to the French coast to help build the so-called Atlantic wall, series of fortification against a possible Allied invasion.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This included my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, his brother as well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jacques as well.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- as a matter of fact, I recall that my father, through a lawyer friend and some money, managed to buy himself into a-- a one-month extension, which we celebrated quite fervently.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after that month, he had no more extension.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then one day, my father's just-- the-- the local police came, escorted my father away, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was left then with-- with my mother and-- and my little brother in that home where we lived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What did my father do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, they didn't tell him they were going to shoot you or kill you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, if you come peacefully, you'll be OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's just for a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And your family will be left undisturbed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you resist, it will be much direr consequences.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So under the circumstances, hoping for the best, people had no choice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no alternative.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was not-- not an option.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
